          <div id="content">
           <div class="inner">
            <p class="pull-quote">
             Promoting the strategic initiatives and special character of Appalachian State University.
            </p>
            <blockquote>
             University Communications manages media relations, critical and crisis communications, serves as an in-house advertising and PR agency for university clients, and promotes and supports major university events and initiatives.
            </blockquote>
            <h2>
             Need help with...?
            </h2>
            <div class="home">
             <ul class="services-list matchheight-container">
              <li class="services-item matchheight-item">
